WEBVTT

00:00:00.199 --> 00:00:15.886
Hey, good morning family. How are y'all doing today? I'm going to deliver a pretty heavy word today; I hope you all are ready for this. I know I haven't been on much; I've been praying about this.

00:00:15.887 --> 00:00:25.437
As a Watchman, it's not always easy to come out and tell you all some of the things that I see, but it's my job, and I'm going to tell you what I see.

00:00:25.438 --> 00:00:32.082
I prayed over this one for quite a while before delivering this because of how heavy this word is.

00:00:32.083 --> 00:00:47.211
I just feel like I should pray before I start because I want you to receive this; it is a very stern warning about things, and I was taken aback by it.

00:00:47.212 --> 00:00:56.903
So, let's just pray real quick and get right into it. Father, I thank You that You speak through my vocal cords and You think through my mind.

00:00:56.904 --> 00:01:07.757
I ask You for none of me and all of You. Every word that I say, Father, I thank You, Holy Spirit, that You help me to deliver it to Your people.

00:01:07.758 --> 00:01:17.254
Father, may this minister to them, and may they take it as the warning that You've given me about the end times and where we are.

00:01:17.255 --> 00:01:26.209
Father, I pray that they would take it to You in prayer and meditate on the Word.

00:01:26.210 --> 00:01:36.806
They won't get into fear; they will meditate on the Word and understand who they are in Christ.

00:01:36.807 --> 00:01:47.618
Lord, I just thank You in Jesus'name, Amen. Now, here comes the word. This is the urgency of what the Lord showed me.

00:01:47.619 --> 00:01:55.830
While I was praying, I put my prayer shawl on and went into deep intercession.

00:01:55.831 --> 00:02:04.970
All of a sudden, the Lord opened my eyes, and in the spirit realm, I was taken over and saw a meeting.

00:02:04.971 --> 00:02:19.278
I'm going to have to be very careful how I deliver this because of the things that I saw.

00:02:19.279 --> 00:02:39.176
I'm going to just say it like this: I want you all to read between the lines as much as possible, because things that I see could jeopardize me and put me in danger.

00:02:39.177 --> 00:02:56.478
So, let's just use a little wisdom here. I was taken up in the spirit and saw a meeting where they were contemplating the next virus.

00:02:56.479 --> 00:03:11.595
They were in a room, and I could see the heads of these leaders; I'll leave it at that. I won't say who I saw, but they were negotiating.

00:03:11.596 --> 00:03:21.112
The obesity epidemic across the world has reached heights beyond anybody's comprehension on purpose.

00:03:21.113 --> 00:03:26.625
Remember when I told you all I saw 350 million people perish?

00:03:26.626 --> 00:03:39.395
350 million would go home, but I didn't know how; I thought it was going to be a COVID-like thing.

00:03:39.396 --> 00:03:52.376
I saw a laboratory. I saw AI computer technology, and AI was creating a super-virus.

00:03:52.377 --> 00:04:01.813
They were using AI to create something more dangerous in the end times than COVID was.

00:04:01.814 --> 00:04:38.876
I could see DNA strands running like computer code. COVID was barely even used in this new strand.

00:04:38.877 --> 00:05:07.837
It was all over here, and they were taking lines from high blood pressure medicine, diabetes medicine, and splicing it into this virus, spanning off of obesity.

00:05:07.838 --> 00:05:26.963
It was being perfected. Skinny people who were not overweight, who took care of themselves, ate right, and maintained a good BMI, were safe.

00:05:26.964 --> 00:05:36.988
They had immunities inside of them somehow to be able to sustain their bodies and not perish.

00:05:36.989 --> 00:05:53.267
But people who were on diabetic medicine, high blood pressure medicine, or high cholesterol medicines were targets.

00:05:53.268 --> 00:06:06.123
If you were heavy, you were a target throughout the whole world.

00:06:06.124 --> 00:06:51.873
I heard them say, 'Obesity is a drain on our economy; it's a drain on society; therefore, we must eliminate this.'I saw a plan to eliminate—and I'm going to be very careful—a group of people because the healthcare system is too much.

00:06:51.874 --> 00:07:06.679
I'm going to put a clip in right here that shows exactly what I saw—how much it's costing the healthcare system.

00:07:06.680 --> 00:07:14.002
The number of morbidly obese people across the United States has skyrocketed to over 30% in the last 20 years.

00:07:14.002 --> 00:07:23.000
What is obesity costing you and me, the taxpayer? Compared to other expenditures, it adds up quickly.

00:07:23.001 --> 00:07:28.143
Flying the president for one year in Air Force One costs us $500 million.

00:07:28.144 --> 00:07:36.976
All costs associated with illegal aliens in California alone cost taxpayers $9 billion a year.

00:07:36.977 --> 00:07:44.043
The 'No Child Left Behind'policy is a staggering $23 billion a year.

00:07:44.044 --> 00:07:50.122
Drunk driving costs $24 billion a year. How does obesity stand up?

00:07:50.123 --> 00:07:59.999
When you add up increased insurance costs, loss of work, and increased Medicare and Medicaid costs, it comes to $80 billion a year.

00:08:00.000 --> 00:08:37.722
That's more than all those other programs combined. Now, I saw Seven Deadly Sins.

00:08:37.723 --> 00:08:41.332
I saw Satan, and he was the head of the meeting. I saw a 'V'like Roman numeral five. At first, there were pillars, and I saw Seven Deadly Sins.

00:08:41.333 --> 00:08:56.875
I'm not familiar with this because I didn't realize this came from the Catholic Church; I'm studying this out before I present it.

00:08:56.876 --> 00:09:16.213
There were two pillars; five were all together—the things that people really recognize, like anger, lust, and wrath.

00:09:16.214 --> 00:09:29.374
I'm sorry, I'll butcher it since I don't have the verse in front of me, but these things the Lord hates: a lying spirit, a heart quick to shed innocent blood.

00:09:29.375 --> 00:09:50.486
Five went like this, and two were right here: slothfulness and gluttony. These were not as upfront as the other sins.

00:09:50.487 --> 00:10:12.603
In the spirit, I saw light shining on the five, but the devil pushed these two—gluttony and slothfulness—to the front to expose them because they weren't as bright.

00:10:12.604 --> 00:10:35.799
He was pushing them to the front, and then I saw him petitioning the Father because of Grace.

00:10:35.800 --> 00:10:51.363
There has been a grace over what we would consider a lack of concern, but there are many heavy people in the Body of Christ.

00:10:51.364 --> 00:11:12.601
He was calling forth all the scriptures, throwing them at the Father, and calling for judgment over obesity, saying this is an open door from seedtime and harvest.

00:11:12.602 --> 00:11:18.943
He was petitioning the open door for judgment concerning this.

00:11:18.944 --> 00:11:55.173
I'm a Watchman, and I'm here to tell you there is a plan for the enemy to design something to wipe people out.

00:11:55.174 --> 00:12:04.317
This is something else I thought was interesting: I saw them using bumblebees.

00:12:04.318 --> 00:12:24.813
These scientists were taking queen bees—big bees—and trying to figure out how to genetically alter them.

00:12:24.814 --> 00:12:47.898
Very strange, and I'm still praying over this. This genetic code using AI for this new thing will line up with the end-time Pale Horse rider.

00:12:47.899 --> 00:13:07.087
After I cried out for mercy, the Lord gave me more time and said, 'Brandon, get the weight off.'I have had a mandate by the Spirit of God to do whatever it takes to get this weight off and keep it off.

00:13:07.088 --> 00:13:16.871
I'm telling you all out of love; it's not to point fingers. I call for Grace.

00:13:16.872 --> 00:13:31.390
Father, forgive me and help me to get the weight off and take care of my body. I don't want to be bound by food addictions anymore.

00:13:31.391 --> 00:13:48.498
I have to reprogram my mind because the value meal at a Burger King or McDonald's was the standard.

00:13:48.499 --> 00:14:07.430
I had to ask myself: what is a right portion? I'm 43 years old and have no clue.

00:14:07.431 --> 00:14:13.939
I'm having to educate myself. Is six ounces of meat a day with lots of vegetables right?

00:14:13.940 --> 00:14:38.005
Some say carnivore, but I need to know what's good for me. This is serious.

00:14:38.006 --> 00:14:46.080
The average diet is 2,000 calories, but you have to eat less than that.

00:14:46.081 --> 00:15:04.180
I got a calorie app and was shocked; I was eating a ton every day, and that's how I got to be over 300 pounds.

00:15:04.181 --> 00:15:19.486
I'm trying to make this a lifestyle because the Spirit of God mandated it.

00:15:19.487 --> 00:15:36.137
The Lord said, 'You're out of time for what's coming.'I felt so much spiritual pressure.

00:15:36.138 --> 00:15:56.283
These 'bad guys'are crazy, just like Hitler was. They have a mandate to lower healthcare costs.

00:15:56.284 --> 00:16:08.466
I'm just trying to warn you and not put you in fear. If you want to say I'm nuts, fine, but at least I told you.

00:16:08.467 --> 00:16:28.086
Jesus is coming. We're in the end of the end. The dark's getting darker, but the light's getting lighter. Jesus is in us, and we have nothing to fear.

00:16:28.087 --> 00:16:41.758
I'm believing God for supernatural healing for every one of you, that you'll be delivered from obesity and whatever they're trying to spice with this AI stuff.

00:16:41.759 --> 00:17:21.290
It's darker than people realize. Don't give up; get this weight off and take care of your bodies because for some of you, it will be life and death.

00:17:21.291 --> 00:17:39.046
We are not to fear because of Psalm 91 and Psalm 23. But when the Lord petitions me to get 100 pounds off as quickly as possible, I listen.

00:17:39.047 --> 00:18:01.404
I saw this going into 2025. We are the Temple of the Holy Ghost, and He dwells on the inside of us.

00:18:01.405 --> 00:18:21.434
He has told me to get the 100 pounds off. I'm down 35 pounds, and my goal for March is another 20 to 30 pounds.

00:18:21.435 --> 00:18:40.999
I'm going to be the healthiest I've ever been, riding my bike and eating right.

00:18:41.000 --> 00:19:25.006
My blood pressure is perfect. The devil is legalistic; he knows the Bible better than we do.

00:19:25.007 --> 00:19:43.390
He’s not Holy Ghost-filled like us, but he knows the Word. I could hear him quoting gluttony scriptures.

00:19:43.391 --> 00:20:04.269
I was frozen in my tracks listening to him petition against me because I was obese. I pleaded the blood and took communion.

00:20:04.270 --> 00:20:25.057
The door was open because of seedtime and harvest, but Grace kept it from happening.

00:20:25.058 --> 00:20:31.726
This seedtime and harvest is going to accelerate beyond anything you can comprehend.

00:20:31.727 --> 00:20:52.918
The sower and the reaper are going to go hand-in-hand in any area of your life.

00:20:52.919 --> 00:21:41.881
It's the acceleration of seedtime and harvest. If you have an urgency to get the weight off, take care of your body.

00:21:41.882 --> 00:21:58.959
Father, I thank You for everyone listening. May this not bring fear but an urgency to take care of their temple.

00:21:58.960 --> 00:22:26.613
I thank You that they have wisdom and revelation knowledge.

00:22:26.614 --> 00:22:33.800
We break the spirit of addiction to junk food in the name of Jesus.

00:22:33.801 --> 00:23:20.933
We take authority over pastas, sweets, and cookies. Father, I thank You that we get the weight off and stay fit.

00:23:20.934 --> 00:23:28.945
I take authority over demonic spirits causing eating disorders.

00:23:28.946 --> 00:24:38.886
We command our minds and hormones to line up with the Word of God. We crucify our flesh daily.

00:24:38.887 --> 00:24:53.912
God has not given us a spirit of fear, but of power, love, and a sound mind.

00:24:53.913 --> 00:25:11.127
I pray blessings and healing over your bodies. You are healed and whole.

00:25:11.128 --> 00:25:37.439
I call you delivered from addictions, from drugs to alcohol to lust.

00:25:37.440 --> 00:25:48.194
You don't have to be bound by the devil. We call forth freedom in the name of Jesus.

00:25:48.195 --> 00:26:14.060
We call for Grace and Mercy. Thank you for being part of this video.

00:26:14.061 --> 00:26:21.098
If you could click that notification bell, it would bless us.

00:26:21.099 --> 00:26:44.439
Thank you for liking and subscribing. We're warning people of the devil's tactics.

00:26:44.440 --> 00:27:32.159
Jesus is coming soon. Put a smile on your face; Jesus loves you so much. We will see you all next time. Bye-bye.

